# Endpoints
##Products
POST  "/products/create"
GET "/products"
GET "/products/{id}
DELETE "/products/delete/{id}"
PUT "/products/edit/{id}"
GET "/products/stock_outed" -->  return(if sotck <= 5)

##Clients
POST "/clients/create"
GET "/clients"
GET "/clients/{id}"
DELETE "/clients/delete/{id}
PUT "/clients/edit/{id}

##Sales
POST "/sales/create"
GET "/sales"
GET "/sales/{id}"
DELETE "/sales/delete/{id}"
PUT "/sales/edit/{id}"
GET "/sales/products/{id}" --> return products from sale
GET "/sales/{date}" --> value & amount of sale of date
GET "/sales/elderly_sale" --> return DTO